scheduled_maintenances.name: Scheduled Maintenance for the EU Region - February 18th from 20:00 UTC to 00:00 UTC

incident_updates.body:
We intend to perform maintenance on Saturday, February 18th from 20:00 UTC to 00:00 UTC (or Saturday, February 18th from 12:00 PST to 16:00 PST). 

Customers in the EU should plan that the synthetics product will be unavailable during the maintenance window. Additionally, customers in the EU may experience irregularities for charts and new account creation. Please note, alert notifications may not be generated during this maintenance period.

All further updates will be posted here on our status page.
